Contract Business Process

After creating a quote, you'll likely want to create a contract. This section tells you how to create a contract from your quote.

You can create a contract through:

* OmniScript flow
* Quote UI

Depending on your role, you can create contracts from different parts of the application:

Internal insurance agent - Quote UI
Vlocity Admin - Vlocity Admin Lighting Experience

Contracts Using the OmniScript Flow

As a Vlocity admin, you can find the Contract Creation OmniScript in the Vlocity OmniScript Designer under:

Type - InsGVB
SubType - CreateContract

The OmniScript generates the proposal document.

How Does It Work?

* Retrieves quote details
* Retrieves account ID and quote ID
* Sets contract status as Draft
* Displays group information, billing info, and contract dates
* Generates proposal
* Creates a contract ID and enrollment census ID

What's Next?

Members can enroll themselves in plans. See the Enrollment Business Process for instructions.

You can also create a contract using the Quote UI or use the Contract Proposal OmniScript to generate proposal documents.
